{"id": 59655, "date": "2025-09-14T04:00:03", "date_gmt": "2025-09-14T11:00:03", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=59655"}, "modified": "2026-05-24T19:07:06", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-25T02:07:06", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-september-14-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/14/kingdom-of-days-september-14-2/", "title": {"rendered": "September 14"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>A scheduled gig at Syracuse University is cancelled to make room for production work on\u00a0<em>The Wild, The Innocent, and the E Street Shuffle\u00a0</em>at 914 Sound Studios in Blauvelt, New York. Today Bruce completes &#8220;New York City Serenade.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/fEQENfRoBgw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDfEQENfRoBgw\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"29411\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1973-09-14-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1973-09-14.jpg?fit=149%2C499&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"149,499\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1973-09-14\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1973-09-14.jpg?fit=149%2C499&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-29411 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1973-09-14.jpg?resize=149%2C499&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"149\" height=\"499\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1973-09-14.jpg?w=149&amp;ssl=1 149w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1973-09-14.jpg?resize=90%2C300&amp;ssl=1 90w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 149px) 100vw, 149px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their second of two shows at the Houston Music Hall, where they play &#8220;A Love So Fine&#8221; for the very last time (at least until it&#8217;s resurrected as &#8220;So Young and in Love&#8221; in the post-Reunion era).</p>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band record &#8220;Ain&#8217;t Good Enough for You&#8221; at The Record Plant in New York City. It will remain in the vault for 33 years until Bruce unearths, completes, and releases it on <em>The Promise.</em></p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/kPg6ZZC3AcY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDkPg6ZZC3AcY\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>It&#8217;s the end of the River Tour with this final show at Cincinnati&#8217;s Riverfront Coliseum, and it&#8217;s Steve Van Zandt&#8217;s last show as a member of the E Street Band for 18 years. Also saying their goodbyes for a while: &#8220;It&#8217;s Hard to Be a Saint in the City&#8221; (next seen 15 years later) and &#8220;The Ties That Bind&#8221; (resurfacing 18 years later).</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/YhD26kZGafI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21088\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1981-09-14/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-14.jpg?fit=2426%2C1514&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2426,1514\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1599230024&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1981-09-14\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-14.jpg?fit=758%2C473&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21088 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-14.jpg?resize=758%2C473&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"473\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-14.jpg?w=2426&amp;ssl=1 2426w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-14.jpg?resize=300%2C187&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-14.jpg?resize=1024%2C639&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-14.jpg?resize=768%2C479&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-14.jpg?resize=1536%2C959&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-14.jpg?resize=2048%2C1278&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1981-09-14.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1983:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band record &#8220;Brothers Under the Bridges (&#8217;83)&#8221; at The Hit Factory in New York City. It will remain in the vaults for fifteen years before seeing release on\u00a0<em>Tracks</em>.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dthkGZiL1gA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDdthkGZiL1gA\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>On Night Three (of six) at the Philadelphia Spectrum on the Born in the U.S.A. Tour, the Miami Horns make a guest appearance.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/6QxyksVy-B4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLJTyL9twk3zARXn4hnEEjOMg9zHewgF_z\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"54433\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/centre_daily_times_1984_09_16_10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Centre_Daily_Times_1984_09_16_10.jpg?fit=2475%2C2170&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2475,2170\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Centre_Daily_Times_1984_09_16_10\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Centre_Daily_Times_1984_09_16_10.jpg?fit=758%2C665&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-54433 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Centre_Daily_Times_1984_09_16_10.jpg?resize=758%2C665&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"665\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Centre_Daily_Times_1984_09_16_10.jpg?w=2475&amp;ssl=1 2475w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Centre_Daily_Times_1984_09_16_10.jpg?resize=300%2C263&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Centre_Daily_Times_1984_09_16_10.jpg?resize=1024%2C898&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Centre_Daily_Times_1984_09_16_10.jpg?resize=768%2C673&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Centre_Daily_Times_1984_09_16_10.jpg?resize=1536%2C1347&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Centre_Daily_Times_1984_09_16_10.jpg?resize=2048%2C1796&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Centre_Daily_Times_1984_09_16_10.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the band play their second of two nights at the Cotton Bowl in Dallas.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/n88PAnzZHZo?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4327\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1985-0914/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1985-0914.jpg?fit=510%2C328&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"510,328\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Picasa&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1376148737&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1985-0914\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1985-0914.jpg?fit=510%2C328&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4327 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1985-0914.jpg?resize=510%2C328&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"510\" height=\"328\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1985-0914.jpg?w=510&amp;ssl=1 510w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1985-0914.jpg?resize=300%2C193&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 510px) 100vw, 510px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1989</strong>: Bruce records &#8220;Viva Las Vegas&#8221; at One on One Recording in Los Angeles.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/quWs4rY-ekc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDquWs4rY-ekc\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1995:\u00a0</strong>Bruce makes a guest appearance with Joe Ely at The Viper Room in West Hollywood, where the two play &#8220;All Just to Get to You.&#8221;</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4329\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1995-0914/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1995-0914.jpg?fit=1000%2C673&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1000,673\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1995-0914\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1995-0914.jpg?fit=758%2C510&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4329 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1995-0914.jpg?resize=758%2C510&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"510\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1995-0914.jpg?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1995-0914.jpg?resize=300%2C202&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1995-0914.jpg?resize=768%2C517&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21089\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1995-09-14/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1995-09-14.jpg?fit=2430%2C1139&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2430,1139\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1599230379&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1995-09-14\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1995-09-14.jpg?fit=758%2C355&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21089 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1995-09-14.jpg?resize=758%2C355&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"355\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1995-09-14.jpg?w=2430&amp;ssl=1 2430w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1995-09-14.jpg?resize=300%2C141&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1995-09-14.jpg?resize=1024%2C480&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1995-09-14.jpg?resize=768%2C360&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1995-09-14.jpg?resize=1536%2C720&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1995-09-14.jpg?resize=2048%2C960&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1995-09-14.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2003:\u00a0</strong>At his Rising show in Chapel Hill, Bruce finally starts acknowledging his TOL/HT/LT era, tour premiering &#8220;Brilliant Disguise,&#8221; and &#8220;Living Proof,&#8221; the latter of which is its first E Street Band performance. The trend will continue throughout the rest of the tour, perhaps not coincidentally while <em>The Essential Bruce Springsteen</em> compilation is in production.</p>\n<div id=\"v-QUWjxN0h-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/QUWjxN0h?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"29414\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2003-09-14a-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2003-09-14a.jpg?fit=1028%2C1854&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1028,1854\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1599230608&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2003-09-14a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2003-09-14a.jpg?fit=568%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-29414 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2003-09-14a.jpg?resize=758%2C1367&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1367\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2003-09-14a.jpg?w=1028&amp;ssl=1 1028w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2003-09-14a.jpg?resize=166%2C300&amp;ssl=1 166w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2003-09-14a.jpg?resize=568%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 568w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2003-09-14a.jpg?resize=768%2C1385&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2003-09-14a.jpg?resize=852%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 852w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21091\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2003-09-14b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2003-09-14b.jpg?fit=977%2C1851&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"977,1851\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1599230656&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2003-09-14b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2003-09-14b.jpg?fit=540%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21091 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2003-09-14b.jpg?resize=758%2C1436&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1436\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2003-09-14b.jpg?w=977&amp;ssl=1 977w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2003-09-14b.jpg?resize=158%2C300&amp;ssl=1 158w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2003-09-14b.jpg?resize=540%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 540w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2003-09-14b.jpg?resize=768%2C1455&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2003-09-14b.jpg?resize=811%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 811w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2007:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band rehearse for their upcoming Magic Tour at Asbury Park&#8217;s Convention Hall.</p>\n<p><strong>2010:\u00a0</strong>As part of the promotional push\u00a0 for the upcoming box set,\u00a0<em>The Promise: The Darkness on the Edge of Town Story</em>, Bruce attends the Toronto International Film Festival for the premiere of the documentary\u00a0<em>The Promise: The Making of the Darkness on the Edge of Town</em>. Before the screening, actor Ed Norton interviews Bruce on stage.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/61LlUqm9rvc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21092\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2010-09-14/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2010-09-14.jpg?fit=1930%2C1649&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1930,1649\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1599230841&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2010-09-14\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2010-09-14.jpg?fit=758%2C648&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21092 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2010-09-14.jpg?resize=758%2C648&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"648\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2010-09-14.jpg?w=1930&amp;ssl=1 1930w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2010-09-14.jpg?resize=300%2C256&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2010-09-14.jpg?resize=1024%2C875&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2010-09-14.jpg?resize=768%2C656&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2010-09-14.jpg?resize=1536%2C1312&amp;ssl=1 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2012:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play a Wrecking Ball show at Nationals Park in Washington, DC, where &#8220;Blinded by the Light&#8221; makes its tour debut and Ali Weinberg (Max&#8217;s daughter) plays the accordion for &#8220;American Land.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/AW2L4kQ9R7Y?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OE5lCqxugZA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2013:\u00a0</strong>The Wrecking Ball Tour continues its South American leg with a stop in Buenos Aires, Argentina, where Bruce opens the show with &#8220;This Little Light of Mine.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/fn9nEbwrAD0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/artWSlhvsqs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HeQyraP6jxo?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2016:\u00a0</strong>The revived River Tour wraps up at Gillette Stadium in Foxborough. The &#8220;autobiography&#8221; theme continues, but there are surprisingly few surprises. &#8220;Rockin&#8217; All Over the World&#8221; is the final tour premiere, and Peter Wolf makes his customary Boston appearance. Bruce delivered a special thank you message to his fans via E Street Radio.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/8trmabdlJeI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/5YTr7oirRNA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4fpAr8l2r4M?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vBYrksfpzBs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"29416\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2016-09-14-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2016-09-14.jpg?fit=959%2C1850&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"959,1850\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1599231455&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quo